Conftop v1.0 (09-18-93 > 10-15-93) - [Private version for my board]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
First version, coded in Arexx by Bobo

09-18-93 { + } I started coding this door.
 - ^^ -  { + } Main source for updating uploads in datafiles.
 - ^^ -  { + } Showing output in conference routine coded.
09-19-93 { + } Now using a configfile.
09-20-93 { + } Now showing total upload stats at the bottom.
09-22-93 { # } Optimized the sourcecode :> Now: 6502 Before: 7523
09-23-93 { * } Now using a own sort routine instaid of using WB's SORT.
               Also abit useless code removed (Now size: 6229)
 - ^^Ā-  { # } Optimized the sourcecode :> Now: 5687 Before: 6229
10-01-93 { ! } You can now choose how many uploaders you want in a conference.
10-02-93 { * } Now using a own showfile routine instaid of using amiexpress's
               that is abit slow.
 - ^^ -  { + } Now configuable playpen paths in configfile.
 - ^^ -  { + } Now changing stat to 'Joining a conf' when running from
               Bull20.txt, and 'Uploading' when running from Filecheck.
 - ^^ -  { ? } Crashed sometimes on A4000/040. Changed some init codes. I
               *think* it works now.
10-03-93 { # } Optimized the sourcecode :> Now: 5439 Before: 6012
               (Alot of useless code & routines removed)
10-07-93 { + } Now you can launch a door after conftop in filecheck.
         { # } ^ NOTE: All type of Doors without AREXX doors works ^
10-10-93 { ! } Didnot give the launched door the right filename.
10-11-93 { * } Changed the output design abit. Now some more chars for
               username and location.
 - ^^ -  { + } Recoded the source so i was able to compile it.

Conftop v1.1 (10-16-93 > 11-02-93) - [Only Available for Betatesters]
