Talked abit with Looby, and we started to make conftop coded in C.

11-02-93 { + } LOOBY: Coded the mainprogram.
11-05-93 { + } BOBO : Coded the message structure to write messages.
11-10-93 { * } LOOBY: Datafile now in binery.
