Conftop v2.2 (02-05-94) - [First Public Release Version]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
First Public release version!

Conftop v2.3 (02-20-94 > 04-19-94) - [Public Release Version]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
02-20-94 { * } BOBO : New design used. Tell me what you think about it!
 - ^^ -  { * } BOBO : Optimized abit. Some useless routines removed.
02-24-94 { ! } BOBO : Conftop did not start the filechecking if a user was
                      found in the excludefile. FIXED!
 - ^^ -  { * } BOBO : The file: Conftop.Stats is no longer needed. It is
                      saved in the Conftop.Data file.
02-25-94 { * } BOBO : Now you can make Conftop resident.
02-26-94 { * } BOBO : The files: Conftop.Playpen & Conftop.Exclude is no
                      longer needed. It is saved in the iconfile.
02-27-94 { * } BOBO : Saved 8 bytes to much for each user in the datafile - FIXED!
03-01-94 { * } BOBO : Removed as much global data as possible from the code.
                      Conftop now requires less memory then before.
 - ^^ -  { ! } BOBO : Conftop was leaking memory at afew places. Most when
                      a error occured. I think i found the most of them, but 
                      please report if you found some more.
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : A new option (tooltype) available. You can now have two
                      or more conferences running on the same datafile. The
                      tooltype in the infofile is called:
                      SHARE_DATA_CNF<conf#>=<conftop datafile>

                      EG: SHARE_DATA_CNF1=BBS:Elite/Conftop.Data
                      - This would make so all uploads in conference one
                        will be tranfered to the datafile in bbs:elite/
 - ^^ -  { * } BOBO : Updated the config program. Now more simple, and not as
                      big as the last one. No user-editor is available in this
                      configprg, so i hope someone will code a external editor
                      for conftop.
03-02-94 { * } BOBO : Coded a convert program to convert the old datafiles to
                      the new format.
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : A new option (tooltype) available. You can now select
                      what door you want to start after conftop.
                      NEXTDOOR=<doorname>  EG: NEXTDOOR=FILECHK
                      - This would try to start a door called FILECHK.
                        You must have it in BBSCMD/
03-05-94 { * } BOBO : Conftop is now totaly running on icons. The whole cfg-
                      program is removed. You must now have a icon in each
                      conference named: Conftop.info. The following tooltypes
                      is available: DAYS,ROWS,MAILUSER,BULLFILE.
 - ^^ -  { ! } BOBO : Conftop did bug sometimes when it was made resident.
                      This problem is fixed!
03-06-94 { + } BOBO : Now if a error occur, it will be written to the callerslog.
03-07-94 { + ) BOBO : New tooltypes in conficon: SHARE_DATA,EXCLUDE_<num>
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : New tooltypes in doorsicon: PLAYPEN_<node>,EXCLUDE_<num>
                      NEXTDOOR. More will be available!
03-08-94 { + } BOBO : New tooltype in conficon: CONFNAME=<name>. If this
                      tooltype is specifed, it will use this conference name
                      instaid of reading it from CONFCONFIG.INFO
03-10-94 { + } BOBO : New tooltype in conficon: SHOW_RESETDATE. If this tooltype
                      is specified the complete resetdate will be shows instaid
                      of eg: Day (1/7).
03-11-94 { ! } BOBO : Fixed quite many bugs in the convert program and maked it
                      safer.
03-13-94 { + } BOBO : New tooltype in conficon: MIN_LIMIT=<size>. If this
                      tooltype is specifed, only users above the <size> will
                      be displayed.  Thanx to DR. G/4WD for the idea!
03-15-94 { + } BOBO : Coded a USEREDITOR so you can edit users in the datafiles.
03-21-94 { ! } BOBO : Fixed the NONSTOP bug.  Thanx to REMO/MST for the report.
03-22-94 { + } BOBO : You can now press CTRL+X in the usereditor to erase all
                      the input.
03-23-94 { * } BOBO : You can now have the tooltypes MIN_LIMIT, BULLFILE,
                      and SHOW_RESETDATE in the global icon.
03-24-94 { * } BOBO : If Conftop couldn't write the message/bulletine, a error
                      will be written to the callerslog.
03-26-94 { ! } BOBO : Now using the tooltypes CONFNAME and MIN_LIMIT when 
                      writing message/bulletine.
03-29-94 { * } BOBO : New Dataformat. You can now change the number of days
                      whenever you want without to reset.  Thanx to RAJ-BAN
                      for the idea/suggestion.
 - ^^ -  { * } BOBO : Now writing: Day (1/7 - Final Results) when conftop
                      is writing mail/bulletine.  Thanx to MOOCHER/FLT for
                      the sugguestion.
 - ^^ -  { ! } BOBO : Now using a own routine to display the header/tailer
                      files. Max 300 chars/line.
03-30-94 { ! } BOBO : Misspelling fixed (Availible->Available)
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : Now you can use both the slot-number and the
                      username at the tooltype EXCLUDE_<num>.
03-31-94 { + } BOBO : You can now enter DAYS=WEEKLY and conftop will always
                      run from Monday->Sunday.
04-02-94 { + } BOBO : New tooltype available: SKIP_EMPTY_LINES. If this
                      tooltype is specified, conftop will not output empty
                      lines.
04-05-94 { ! } BOBO : Forgot to send the carrage return in my displayfile
                      routine.  Thanx to Dee/Delight for the bugreport!
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : New tooltype: FROMUSER. Here you can specify a own
                      user the message should be written from.
 - ^^ -  { + } BOBO : New tooltype: SUBJECT. Here you can specify a own
                      subject for the message.
04-07-94 { ! } BOBO : Conftop read the config two times each time a user
                      was joining a conference or uploading a file.
04-12-94 { * } BOBO : Changed, fixed and updated the WEEKLY feature.
                      Please report if this work correctly now!
04-16-94 { + } BOBO : Conftop now checks if the upload is private. If it is
                      conftop will skip the update.
04-19-94 { - } BOBO : Registration routines removed.
                      Final size: 25976 (Source: 33123 with comments)
